               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols. 4ra-130ra)
                     II) Malkǝʾa Takla Hāymānot “Image of Takla Haymanot” (fols. 130rb-132va)
